    <standards>
Recipe uses manual browser testing for web UI stories (no automated JavaScript testing framework currently). Testing standards:
- Manual testing across browsers: Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge
- Device testing: Desktop (1920x1080), Tablet (768px), Mobile (375px)
- Accessibility testing: Keyboard navigation (Tab, Enter, Esc), screen reader compatibility
- Performance validation: Conversion timing (<100ms target), UI responsiveness (60fps interactions)
- Cross-browser feature detection: AbortController support check with graceful degradation
    </standards>
    <locations>
      <location>web/static/index.html - Manual browser testing</location>
